1
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,760
Ah!

2
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:42,760
Why did the Demon King open his eyes?

3
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:46,120
Wasn't he supposed to wake up only after the female lead cared for him tirelessly for three days and nights?

4
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:47,320
His eyes are so scary.

5
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,200
What should I do?

6
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,440
He saw it.

7
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,200
The demon has awoken.

8
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,120
Leave immediately.

9
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:53,320
World Consciousness,

10
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,600
didn't you say that having just broken the seal,

11
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,860
he would be as weak as an ordinary person?

12
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:58,620
World Consciousness!

13
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:01,250
Say something, World Consciousness!

14
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,080
That was close.

15
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:10,880
There was a bug here

16
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:11,960
that actually tried

17
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,200
to harm you.

18
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,280
Good thing I reacted quickly

19
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:17,120
and stabbed it to death with one strike.

20
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,120
It was no trouble.

21
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:20,440
No need to thank me for saving your life.

22
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:24,160
You seem to be perfectly fine,

23
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,920
so I'll be going now.

24
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,880
The Daughter of the World is approaching.

25
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:29,000
She must be stopped.

26
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,600
Oh, right.

27
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:30,800
If I keep them from meeting,

28
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,930
I can change the original trajectory.

29
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,530
Lu Danyu,

30
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,039
why are you here?

31
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,120
I...

32
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,060
It's getting late.

33
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,640
I saw you weren't back yet,

34
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,840
so I came out to look for you.

35
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,479
Oh, right.

36
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,250
You've been out for so long.

37
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:49,520
Um,

38
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,640
the nether demons,

39
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,100
how did you deal with them?

40
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,120
Was it dangerous?

41
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,120
Let's hurry back.

42
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,640
We have protective magical artifacts.

43
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,280
How could mere low-level nether demons

44
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,240
be dangerous?

45
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,800
And he is...

46
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,240
He...

47
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,199
I...

48
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,560
I am Li Yuan,

49
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,640
a cultivator from the Yinglong Sect.

50
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,370
On Li Island,

51
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:18,000
I was besieged and injured by nether demons.

52
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,440
As expected of the Demon King.

53
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,680
He's establishing his identity so quickly.

54
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,280
I hope the fairy will be generous

55
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,680
and bestow upon me a pill.

56
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,050
Fellow cultivator,

57
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:31,120
Since you were injured by nether demons,

58
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,520
how could we not save you?

59
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,880
In every previous cycle,

60
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,020
the demon was saved with this excuse.

61
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,720
Given the Daughter of the World's temperament,

62
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:47,400
She definitely couldn't ignore a person like this.

63
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,800
He's really shameless,

64
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,480
grasping the female lead's character so well.

65
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,400
It's hard that I can't expose him right now.

66
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,200
With the little power the female lead and I have,

67
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,640
it's probably not enough for him to even bother.

68
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,880
You are right to be concerned.

69
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,160
He has slightly recovered.

70
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:02,240
He is indeed not someone you can deal with.

71
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,880
Fellow Cultivator Li, if you don't mind,

72
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,120
you can come back to Danyang Valley with me

73
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,050
to treat the rest of your injuries.

74
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:18,060
Thank you both for taking me in and taking care of me.

75
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,600
Especially

76
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:22,320
Miss Lu, who found me in deep trouble.

77
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,170
In the future, I, Li,

78
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,570
will definitely repay you.

79
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,170
Consciousness.

80
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,360
Why is he talking to me?

81
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,840
Why does it sound to me like...

82
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,400
'You're dead'?

83
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,200
It sounds like that to me too.

84
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,240
The fairy is kind-hearted.

85
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:41,840
I, Li,

86
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,290
will keep it in mind.

87
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,680
Knowing when I would break the seal,

88
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,760
They knew the location of my birth,

89
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:52,880
and even knew

90
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,960
that I am at my weakest right now.

91
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,600
Who sent her?

92
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,600
Who

93
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,760
could have calculated all this?

94
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,080
Danyu,

95
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,520
where did you go?

96
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:15,040
Do you know that you were just cured of poison?

97
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,680
Good thing Xiaoxue found you.

98
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,760
If you do this again,

99
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,160
I'll...

100
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,320
I won't do it again.

101
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,360
Our Danyu

102
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,530
has really grown up.

103
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,400
Who is this?

104
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,880
While I was looking for Lu Danyu,

105
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,560
I met this Yinglong Sect cultivator, Li Yuan.

106
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,220
Brother Li.

107
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:34,840
He

108
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,360
was injured by a Nether Demon.

109
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,520
His injuries are severe.

110
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,380
When I went out,

111
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,960
I only brought some emergency pills.

112
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,200
I couldn't fully cure him,

113
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,930
so I had to bring him back first.

114
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,330
You did the right thing.

115
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,760
I'll help you take care of Brother Li.

116
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,280
Come.

117
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:51,960
Please.

118
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:56,720
It seems the plot is still heading towards healing the Demon King.

119
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,650
Since this node cannot be changed,

120
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,840
we can only wait for the next opportunity.

121
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,400
I consumed too much energy

122
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,240
and need to sleep for a while.

123
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,360
During this time,

124
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:09,000
you must maintain the relationship between the Son and Daughter of the World.

125
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,000
Don't let the demon take advantage.

126
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,840
If before I wake up,

127
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:15,240
the Daughter of the World has already sided with the Demon Lord,

128
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,440
we will be in trouble.

129
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,520
Lastly,

130
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:20,020
try not to openly provoke the Demon Lord.

131
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,280
Wait for me to wake up.

132
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,560
But didn't I just provoke him?

133
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,780
Take care of yourself.

134
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:29,100
World Consciousness.

135
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,490
Consciousness.

136
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,560
Now,

137
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,800
do I have to save myself?

138
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,080
Um,

139
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,120
Sister Mu.

140
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,330
Lu Danyu.

141
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,330
You are very strange today.

142
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,000
Before,

143
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,810
you always called me Miss Mu

144
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,490
or Divine Doctor Mu.

145
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,160
Such an intimate term as Sister Mu,

146
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,680
it's the first time I've heard it.

147
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:18,480
It shouldn't be just because of a mere Baijie Pill.

148
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,160
I gave you so many

149
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,960
elixirs more precious than this before,

150
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:26,090
and I never saw you show any gratitude.

151
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,800
Now you are acting like this,

152
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,800
it makes me a little uncomfortable.

153
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,400
You'd better go back to the way you were.

154
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,280
What?

155
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,010
I was just being polite.

156
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,560
Did I break character?

157
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,330
With this identity,

158
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,250
was I a two-faced bitch before?

159
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,200
Now,

160
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,720
not only do I have to save myself from the Demon King,

161
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,520
but I also have to save myself from the female lead?

162
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,840
No, Sister Mu.

163
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,080
I really think

164
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,040
you are a maverick woman.

165
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,120
Beautiful, kind-hearted,

166
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,159
and intelligent.

167
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:53,880
And also...

168
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:56,210
Are you going to play the same trick again?

169
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:58,680
I told you.

170
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,200
It's your business that you like Wei Wuzhou.

171
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,880
But your two-faced behavior

172
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,320
is really disgusting.

173
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,740
That brainless Wei Wuzhou might fall for it,

174
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,520
but I won't.

175
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,960
If you continue to be so disgusting,

176
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:13,020
I will kick you out of Danyang Valley.

177
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,400
So,

178
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,400
I'm not cannon fodder.

179
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,280
I'm the vicious female supporting character?

180
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,160
I-

181
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:24,360
No wonder the consciousness worried that the heroine would turn to the Demon King.

182
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,760
With such a troublemaker,

183
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:28,040
it's no wonder the main characters' relationship is bad.

184
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,080
She likes Wei Wuzhou,

185
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,760
but I don't.

186
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:31,880
Anyway,

187
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,400
I can't let them break up.

188
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,600
I need to save myself.

189
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,840
Sister Mu.

190
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,320
You really misunderstood.

191
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,920
My affection for Brother Wuzhou

192
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,180
is strictly familial.

193
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,720
He is the brother I grew up with.

194
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,640
How could I really like him?

195
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,480
That is not what you said before.

196
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,760
Before,

197
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,880
I was just being impulsive.

198
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:53,740
Seeing Brother Wuzhou treat you so well, Sister Mu,

199
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,720
I was jealous

200
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,440
and spoke without thinking.

201
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,000
After all, growing up,

202
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,760
he has never treated other girls this well.

203
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:04,680
But,

204
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,320
today,

205
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,320
I almost died.

206
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,280
It was your elixir

207
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,450
that saved me again.

208
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,410
I am truly very grateful to you.

209
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:14,880
So,

210
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,480
I hope you can forget my past mistakes.

211
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:19,640
Let's get along well from now on.

212
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,500
As long as you don't...

213
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,340
As long as you don't

214
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,000
make those old mistakes,

215
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,680
I won't hold it against you.

216
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,200
You're so good to me, Sister.

217
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:33,480
I knew you wouldn't hold it against me.

218
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,159
By the way,

219
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:35,919
that...

220
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,480
demon—

221
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,760
I mean,

222
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,440
the person who was saved,

223
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,799
how is he doing now?

224
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,160
Although the wound looks scary,

225
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,640
it's just a superficial injury.

226
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:48,900
It's nothing serious.

227
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:52,560
Is there absolutely no chance

228
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,250
of his life being in danger?

229
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,200
You underestimate our Danyang Valley.

230
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,800
After taking our Heart-Protecting Pill,

231
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,800
his internal injuries were immediately stabilized.

232
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,130
His life is in no danger.

233
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:03,640
Listen, sister.

234
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,160
You don't need to be so defensive.

235
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,320
I really didn't underestimate you.

236
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,640
If you're still worried...

237
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,040
Just go in and take a look.

238
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,280
Go in and take a look?

239
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,800
How could I dare?

240
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,240
What should I do?
